OL,3,CMan sets underwear on fire as part of
OL,4,Cthreats against his family
OL,6,FA man set fire to his own underwear as
OL,7,Fpart of a campaign of threats and
OL,8,Fdemands for cash from his family.
OL,10,FJordan Donnelly, 23, set fire to a
OL,11,Fnumber of items in his flat in
OL,12,FNorthwich, Cheshire, and even
OL,13,Fthreatened to blow it up if family
OL,14,Fmembers did not send him money.
OL,16,FDonnelly, of Chapel Court, is now
OL,17,Fserving a 21-month jail sentence after
OL,18,Fadmitting threatening to destroy his
OL,19,Fown property and endangering life.
