OL,6,FChester Crown Court was told that on
OL,7,F11 December 2023, police received a
OL,8,Fcall from Cheshire Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService reporting that a man had been
OL,10,Fsetting fire to paper inside his own
OL,11,Fproperty.
OL,13,FOfficers were told Donnelly had been
OL,14,Fsending abusive messages to family
OL,15,Fmembers and even sent videos of him
OL,16,Fsetting fire to a number of items,
OL,17,Fincluding letters, the flat carpet,
OL,18,Fsofa and his own underwear.
