OL,3,CMan sets underwear on fire as part of
OL,4,Cthreats against his family
OL,6,FWhen officers arrived at the address,
OL,7,FDonnelly told them he had burnt some
OL,8,Ftoast. However, a subsequent search of
OL,9,Fthe address found numerous burnt
OL,10,Fpieces of paper scattered across the
OL,11,Fflat and fire damage to the carpet and
OL,12,Fthe sofa.
OL,14,FDonnelly was arrested and a search of
OL,15,Fhis phone revealed more messages
OL,16,Fcontaining abusive language sent by
OL,17,Fhim via Facebook Messenger.
