OL,6,FHe answered "no comment" to all
OL,7,Fquestions directed toward him when
OL,8,Finterviewed and was subsequently
OL,9,Fcharged.
OL,11,FFollowing the sentencing, Detective
OL,12,FConstable Alli Connolly said:
OL,13,F"Donnelly not only caused considerable
OL,14,Fstress to his own family through the
OL,15,Fsending of numerous threatening and
OL,16,Fabusive messages, but he also caused
OL,17,Fsubstantial damage to his own home,
OL,18,Fwhich was also a housing association-
OL,19,Fowned property.
